name: Vending Machine
description:
They arrived at a downtown district that looked very unfamiliar, the district was named StoneFruitz.

Rai & Raka decided to rest first, looking for a cold drink vending machine to just refresh their bodies. A black cat is seen following them, the cat is sitting in front of them watching Rai & Raka.

Rai greeted the cat "Hi" but Raka mocked the cat, the cat was silent and replied "Meow"

What will they do with the cat?
See you in the last episode.


* This description was translated using google translate
